@page "/"

<PageTitle>Bouwdepot Invoice Validator</PageTitle>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Bouwdepot Invoice Validator</h1>
                    
                    <p class="lead">
                        Welcome to the Bouwdepot Invoice Validator. This application helps you verify if an invoice 
                        is related to home improvement expenses and check for possible fraud or tampering.
                    </p>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Features:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>PDF invoice extraction with advanced text recognition</li>
                        <li>Verification of invoice authenticity and checking for tampering signs</li>
                        <li>AI-powered validation of home improvement relevance using Gemini Flash 2.0</li>
                        <li>Fraud detection to identify suspicious invoice characteristics</li>
                        <li><strong>NEW:</strong> Bouwdepot-specific rules validation checking:</li>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Quality improvement rule (improves home value)</li>
                            <li>Permanent attachment rule (permanently fixed to house)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <li><strong>NEW:</strong> Verduurzamingsdepot validation for sustainability improvements:</li>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Insulation (facade, roof, floor, pipes)</li>
                            <li>High-efficiency glazing (HR++)</li>
                            <li>Energy-efficient doors and frames</li>
                            <li>Heat pumps, solar cells, and ventilation systems</li>
                        </ul>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="text-center mt-5">
                        <a href="/invoice-upload" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4">
                            <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf me-2"></i> Validate Invoice
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
